Traverse from 0 to n/2 to find the smallest left side chunk and right side chunk which are equal.
Once you find it(🧒 👤.........👤 🧒), add 2\xA0(🧒🧒) to solution and then recursively call the function for remaining string(👤..........👤 ).
Terminating conditions:
a. Either string will be empty : return 0 
b. Or there are no more equal right and left chunks left (just a single lonely chunk 🙇‍♂️ ): return 1

